2 different pets are kept: lizard, rabbit
1. the polish is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
3. the polish is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Cigar          | prince | alhambra |
| Music-Genre   | blues     | folk      |
| Nationality   | malaysian | polish    |
| Pet           | lizard    | rabbit    |

